With a detective (Donnie Wahlberg) convinced he is the murderer, Jamie returns to his childhood town of Raven\'s Fair, where a legendary ghost story is told. The story is about a woman named Mary Shaw, a ventriloquist who was murdered after being suspected of murder. She was buried with her massive amount of dolls and puppets as well. After her death, it seems she has been taking revenge on the townspeople, when numerous families are found dead with their tongues missing. Jamie takes it upon himself to solve the legend and curse before he becomes the next victim.";s:10:"date_added";s:1:"0";s:8:"modified";s:19:"2008-04-16 07:02:04";s:11:"modified_by";s:2:"62";s:5:"image";s:132:"a:2:{s:5:"image";s:40:"directcron/img_pictures/deadsilenced.jpg";s:9:"thumbnail";s:42:"directcron/img_thumbnails/deadsilenced.jpg";}";s:5:"video";N;s:8:"item_url";s:0:"";s:12:"templatefile";s:7:"oneitem";s:8:"metadesc";s:886:"Horror, Dead Silence" is a movie that I had been highly anticipating ever since I saw the trailer for it. I just got back from seeing it and I wasn\'t disappointed at all. The film follows Jamie Ashen (Ryan Kwanten), who, after receiving a mysterious puppet, returns home to find his wife, Lisa (Laura Regan) murdered. With a detective (Donnie Wahlberg) convinced he is the murderer, Jamie returns to his childhood town of Raven\'s Fair, where a legendary ghost story is told. The story is about a woman named Mary Shaw, a ventriloquist who was murdered after being suspected of murder. She was buried with her massive amount of dolls and puppets as well. After her death, it seems she has been taking revenge on the townspeople, when numerous families are found dead with their tongues missing. Jamie takes it upon himself to solve the legend and curse before he becomes the next victim.";s:8:"meta_key";s:21:"Horror, Dead Silence ";s:10:"searchkeys";s:20:"Donnie Wahlberg,Saw ";s:6:"visits";s:3:"428";s:9:"published";s:1:"1";s:8:"ordering";s:1:"0";s:8:"featured";s:1:"0";s:14:"featured_